@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<div class="about-page">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="about-page-hero">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>We believe in the power of quality footwear to transform your everyday experience. Every pair tells a story of craftsmanship and attention to detail.</p>
    </div>

    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542291026-7eec264c27ff?w=1200&q=80" alt="Our Story" class="about-page-img">

    <!-- Our Story -->
    <div class="about-section-block">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>Founded in 2020, NEXT HORIZON started with a simple belief — premium footwear should be accessible to everyone who values quality and design. What began as a small curation of hand-picked styles has grown into a trusted destination for footwear enthusiasts across the globe.</p>
        <p>Every shoe in our collection is carefully selected by our team of design experts, evaluated not just for aesthetics but for the craftsmanship, comfort, and materials that go into each pair.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission -->
    <div class="about-section-block">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>To connect people with footwear that genuinely elevates their daily life. We are relentless in our pursuit of quality — partnering only with brands that share our commitment to excellence, ethical production, and lasting design.</p>
        <p>We don't just sell shoes. We help you find the ones that fit who you are.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="about-stats-row">
        <div>
            <div class="about-stat-num">50K+</div>
            <div class="about-stat-label">Happy Customers</div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div class="about-stat-num">200+</div>
            <div class="about-stat-label">Curated Styles</div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div class="about-stat-num">4.9★</div>
            <div class="about-stat-label">Average Rating</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
